{"TopicId":160767,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Katyusha Rocket Launcher Truck (with free pivoting stock ball-joint hinge)","CreatedByName":"Krog34","CreatedById":160084,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-18T05:39:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Krog34","CreatedById":160084,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-18T05:39:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:36px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#e74c3c;\u0022\u003EKatyusha Rocket Launcher Truck\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:36px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#e74c3c;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022FPEgMoH.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/FPEgMoH.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:36px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/letmeparkthatforyou/Katyusha-Rocket-Launcher-Truck-----wFreePivot\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKerbalX Craft File Here\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:36px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#e74c3c;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022UTt8MY3.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/UTt8MY3.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003EI\u0027ve had this idea for a long time about connecting a lot \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E controllers and a claw in some manner in order to create \u003Cstrong\u003Esome sort of stock hinge\u003C/strong\u003E. I\u0027ve finally gotten this setup to work nice and smooth. A grip of different wheels act as a nice cushy bearing housing for the weapons cylinder.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:36px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#e74c3c;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PbpEfgF.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/PbpEfgF.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003EIn the above GIF you can see the \u003Cstrong\u003Esetup process\u003C/strong\u003E. Stage once to activate fuel cells and\u00A0separate the craft, the cylinder separates from the bottom while the weapons rack separates and then re-attaches at the top ultimately creating two separate crafts. After setup, control from the probe core at the front to take proper control of the weapons rack. \u003Cu\u003EMake sure \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E is on or you\u0027ll have no control!\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:36px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#e74c3c;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022uxonNiL.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/uxonNiL.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs a \u003Cstrong\u003Eunique feature, you can toggle the \u0022Free Pivot\u0022\u003C/strong\u003E option on the claw in order to take advantage of free motion as the above GIF shows. You can do this with the rockets loaded, but it is more of a balancing act. The Ore Tanks at the front of the rack act as a counterweight and \u003Cstrong\u003Ecan be dumped by pressing 2\u003C/strong\u003E when necessary.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-18T05:40:35Z\u0022 title=\u002205/18/2017 05:40  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 18, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Krog34\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-18T05:40:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s really cool! Seems though not the most stable of things... (when in free pivot)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Combatsmithen","CreatedById":146407,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-18T14:06:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDang thats\u00A0goood\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-18T16:02:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCertainly not a katyusha, but the pivot system is cool.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MiffedStarfish","CreatedById":175356,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-18T19:04:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd here I was thinking you had made some boring truck to transport rockets to the launchpad. Stock hinges and stock weapons, my two favorite things in one ship! Brilliant craft, I\u0027ll have to try it out. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Moose In Your House","CreatedById":177101,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-20T15:24:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the craft but how did you make those gifs?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Krog34","CreatedById":160084,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-22T17:01:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223062315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160767\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221495293876\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177101\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Moose In Your House\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/20/2017 at 8:24 AM, The Moose In Your House said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the craft but how did you make those gifs?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI edited the GIF to be the length and content I wanted with Sony Vegas (though any editor will work) and then I used my favorite site,\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://ezgif.com/maker\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EEzGIF\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0to convert a video into a GIF. The kicker is optimizing the GIF so it\u0027s closer to 10 or 20MB instead of like 60MB\u002B\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHope that helps!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-22T17:03:16Z\u0022 title=\u002205/22/2017 05:03  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 22, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Krog34\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MiffedStarfish","CreatedById":175356,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-23T18:05:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI took your idea of a missile turret with vertical and horziontal hinges and made my own, smaller I-Beam version, to be mounted on warships.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/qDXntkEOHbQ?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the idea! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}